Easily implemented methods for sampling from multivariate distributions,
 
\begin_inset Formula $p(\theta_{1},...,\theta_{k})$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Requirements: Easily sampled full conditional posteriors:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
